name: MIMIC
description:
Built over a long time based on lighting and details I liked from models as I went. I made this for general use but it leans NSFW and I use it for all my NSFW posts in r/sdnsfw

Leans photoreal / semi-real but can be stylized

Hands will be your biggest problem. You'll have to cherrypick or inpaint.
